{"about_the_game":"<strong>All you know is forward at this point. Even if the world is against you. You're the intruder.</strong><br><br>Intruder Alert is a 2D action-stealth adventure combined with multiple other genres packed into a single game. You play as a circle. A shape determined to complete its mission. Stealthily avoid other shapes, defeat them when necessary, and complete various tasks along your journey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UNFORGIVING</h2>Deaths are inevitable. If you get annoyed easily, this game probably isn't for you. Just know that it's a skill issue.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VARYING GAMEPLAY</h2>From stealth to RPG to infinite runner, you'll be shocked to learn what the next level has in store for you as the gameplay suddenly changes. Be prepared.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REPLAYABLE</h2>Play through a wide range of levels, and time yourself for each one. Try to beat your fastest time if you can.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BOSSES</h2>Every difficult game needs a boss or two. Or three. Or four. Or five. Maybe just five. Don't worry, though; you'll have more trouble just getting to them.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Lookin' Good!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2722760/a6b95971302460a4ab66c4393e84ef7aebc3c0a5.jpg"},{"name":"Inevitable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2722760/716781282a017c8df49b02c04f6519dac7e87531.jpg"},{"name":"Unlucky","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2722760/3218069170e5720ce8127ec257665bff47167df8.jpg"},{"name":"Skill Issue","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2722760/b2020f6a2989b2746e2ad190e38d587e1e3c6a6b.jpg"},{"name":"Baller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2722760/270634df179490608bc5db8bddef886d0da2ad93.jpg"},{"name":"Legends Never Die","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/app